{"schema_version":"1","crate":"ml_kem","version":"1.0.0","id":"21db298939353308","name":"ML_KEM.NTT_Zetas","qualified_name":"ML_KEM.NTT_Zetas","kind":"ada_package","location":{"file":"src/ml_kem-ntt_zetas.ads","line":1,"column":9},"code":"package ML_KEM.NTT_Zetas","documentation":{"description":"Zetas are precomputed Montgomery-domain twiddle factors for the\n256-point NTT over Z_q[X]/(X^256 + 1) with q = 3329. By\nconstruction they satisfy |z| < q (in fact |z| <= 1659 in this\ntable). Constraining the subtype to range -(Q-1) .. (Q-1) lets\nSPARK use this fact in product-bound proofs without per-element\ncase analysis."},"subtypes":[{"id":"c4e5b2d0a3744aa9","name":"Zeta_Type","qualified_name":"ML_KEM.NTT_Zetas.Zeta_Type","kind":"ada_subtype","location":{"file":"src/ml_kem-ntt_zetas.ads","line":13,"column":12},"code":"subtype Zeta_Type is I16 range -(Q - 1) .. (Q - 1);"}],"constants":[{"id":"eccb934d7b7e74dc","name":"Brv_Shift","qualified_name":"ML_KEM.NTT_Zetas.Brv_Shift","kind":"ada_constant","location":{"file":"src/ml_kem-ntt_zetas.ads","line":33,"column":4},"code":"Brv_Shift : constant array (0 .. 6) of Natural := [7, 6, 5, 4, 3, 2, 1];"},{"id":"9bfc71e007d5495f","name":"Zetas","qualified_name":"ML_KEM.NTT_Zetas.Zetas","kind":"ada_constant","location":{"file":"src/ml_kem-ntt_zetas.ads","line":15,"column":4},"code":"Zetas : constant array (0 .. 127) of Zeta_Type :=\n  [-1044,   -758,   -359, -1517,  1493,  1422,   287,   202,\n     -171,    622,  1577,   182,   962, -1202, -1474,  1468,\n   …\n     -108,  -308,   996,   991,   958, -1460,  1522,  1628];"}]}